Pronunciation[edit]

  • (Classical) IPA(key): /in.terˈstin.ɡʷoː/, [ɪn̪.t̪ɛrˈst̪ɪŋ.ɡʷoː]
  • (Ecclesiastical) IPA(key): /in.terˈstin.ɡwo/, [in̪.t̪ɛrˈst̪iŋ.ɡwɔ]

Verb[edit]

interstinguō (present infinitive interstinguere, perfect active interstīnxī, supine interstīnctum); third conjugation

  1. I extinguish
  2. I kill

Verb[edit]

interstinguō (present infinitive interstinguere, supine interstīnctum); third conjugation, no perfect stem

  1. I mark off, I divide
  2. I nuance
  3. I checker, I variegate
